<h4>HOUSE COMMITTEES</h4>
<hr />
<h4><span class="text-primary">CLIMATE CHANGE</span></h4>
<div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>

<p><strong>JURISDICTION: </strong>All matters directly and principally relating to policies and programs to mitigate the impact of climate change to the environment, as characterized by global warming, greenhouse effect, rising of sea levels and shifts in meteorological patterns.</p><p><strong>CHAIRPERSON :</strong></p><img src='../members/images/18th/chatto-e.jpg' alt='Hon. Chatto, Edgar M.' title='Hon. Chatto, Edgar M.' 
        class='img-thumbnail img-responsive pull-left img-margin' width='145px' height='100px' /><h5><a href='../members/search.php?id=chatto-e' title='More info about our CHAIRPERSON'>Chatto, Edgar M.</a></h5><p>District Representative<br />Bohol, 1st District<br /></p><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><p><strong>MEMBERS : </strong>20</p><p><strong>COMMITTEE OFFICE : </strong></p><blockquote class='block-ital-sm'><p>3/F RVM Building, House of Representatives, Quezon City<br />Telephone no. 951-5455<br />Committee Secretary: Mr. Erwin Lara<br /></p></blockquote><p class="text-warning">SOURCE: Committee on Rules (Committee Membership) : BIS (Bills Referred) : Committee Affairs Department (Schedule of Meetings) : Engineering Division (Committees' Location/Telephone) : <abbr title="Information and Communication Technology Service">ICTS</abbr> (Website Maintenance)</p>
